peted in the previous season, along with one new club:\n*[[Blidworth Welfare F.C.|Folk House Old Boys]]\n\n===League table===\n{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|res_col_header=QR\n|winpoints=2\n\n|team1=BOR|name_BOR=[[Borrowash Victoria A.F.C.|Borrowash Victoria]]\n|team2=STA|name_STA=[[Staveley Works F.C.|Staveley Works]]\n|team3=ARK|name_ARK=[[Arnold Kingswell F.C.|Arnold Kingswell]]\n|team4=SUT|name_SUT=[[Sutton Trinity F.C.|Sutton Trinity]]\n|team5=FOL|name_FOL=[[Blidworth Welfare F.C.|Folk House Old Boys]]\n|team6=LEG|name_LEG=[[Long Eaton Grange F.C.|Long Eaton Grange]]\n|team7=OAK|name_OAK=[[Oakham United F.C. (Nottinghamshire)|Oakham United]]\n|team8=LIN|name_LIN=[[Linby Colliery F.C.|Linby Colliery]]\n|team9=CRE|name_CRE=[[Creswell Colliery F.C.|Creswell Colliery]]\n|team10=LEU|name_LEU=[[Long Eaton United F.C.|Long Eaton United]] reserves\n|team11=RET|name_RET=[[Retford Rail F.C.|Retford Rail]]\n|team12=ETR|name_ETR=[[Eastwood Town F.C.|Eastwood Town]] reserves\n|team13=CAR|name_CAR=[[Carrvale United F.C.|Carrvale United]]\n|team14=ARR|name_ARR=[[Arnold F.C.|Arnold]] reserves\n|team15=ROL|name_ROL=[[Hucknall Rolls Leisure F.C.|Rolls Royce (Hucknall)]]\n|team16=ATT|name_ATT=[[Attenborough F.C.|Attenborough]]\n\n|win_ARK=17|draw_ARK=8|loss_ARK=5|gf_ARK=71|ga_ARK=37\n|win_ARR=7|draw_ARR=7|loss_ARR=16|gf_ARR=42|ga_ARR=58\n|win_ATT=6|draw_ATT=4|loss_ATT=20|gf_ATT=25|ga_ATT=72\n|win_BOR=22|draw_BOR=6|loss_BOR=2|gf_BOR=79|ga_BOR=32\n|win_CAR=9|draw_CAR=5|loss_CAR=16|gf_CAR=38|ga_CAR=56\n|win_CRE=8|draw_CRE=9|loss_CRE=13|gf_CRE=37|ga_CRE=53\n|win_ETR=6|draw_ETR=11|loss_ETR=13|gf_ETR=45|ga_ETR=61\n|win_FOL=15|draw_FOL=6|loss_FOL=9|gf_FOL=42|ga_FOL=28\n|win_LEG=13|draw_LEG=7|loss_LEG=10|gf_LEG=42|ga_LEG=40\n|win_LEU=10|draw_LEU=4|loss_LEU=16|gf_LEU=41|ga_LEU=57\n|win_LIN=10|draw_LIN=7|loss_LIN=13|gf_LIN=41|ga_LIN=44\n|win_OAK=11|draw_OAK=10|loss_OAK=9|gf_OAK=43|ga_OAK=45\n|win_RET=9|draw_RET=5|loss_RET=16|gf_RET=40|ga_RET=50\n|win_ROL=8|draw_ROL=4|loss_ROL=18|